public class HierarchicalVDEAPreferenceRelations extends Object implements PreferenceRelations<HierarchicalVDEAProblemData>
Verifies the presence of the necessary and possible efficiency preference relations for problems with hierarchical structure of inputs and outputs and VDEA model
